{
  "stem": "18102.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was a big danger in making that decision, but-- the decision which I partook in, as if my parents cared of my opinion.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they told me that the decision would have to be made whether to apply-- now that he got his visa to Japan-- or not and that the danger was that if they connected it up to who we really were that the chances were very good that we would be arrested and gone, sent to Siberia.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How did you vote?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I voted to go, because that's what my parents told me they were voting.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I voted with them, and it became a unanimous vote to apply.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, he was laying low.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "By then there was very little writing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was mostly surviving.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was a, he was a, a survivor, with others, in the forests surrounding Lithuania or surrounding Kaunas and would occasionally go into Kaunas.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's how he learned about the Japanese foreign ministry there and the fact that the Japanese [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] ambassador, Sugihara, could grant visas to those who applied.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we got to Vilna it was in September of 1939, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] because we were under German rule only for a couple of weeks.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it had to be towards the end of September that we got to Vilna.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we stayed there from 1941 September-- 1939, sorry, September, through late 1940.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "By that, I mean probably December, when we left for Moscow.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it was over a year that we remained in Vilna.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, they were issued in August of 1940.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we had to then apply for permission to leave.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The visa in itself didn't get you out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The visa only was the ticket to get out.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
